<D>__{buster, for crying out loud, i reminded her the indians used to own fakahatchee. look, we'll deal with all this at trial.}
<A>__{buster waves a dismissive hand at lerner, walks away. vinson shrugs, stubs his cigarette, follows buster. lerner and laroche stand there a moment. lerner walks off. laroche cracks his neck. a charmingly shy orlean approaches.}
<C>__{orlean}
<D>__{mr. laroche?}
